body:
There are couple of issues from a **data modeling** perpective. 

First of all, you shouldn't separate Lat, Lon, Timestamp in 3 lists. A easier approach would be something like 
`[{
       "lat": float,
       "lon": float,
       "timestamp": long
    }
  ]`

The analysis part gets much easier, if done like that. _(Don't know whether the following applies for Realm)_ Moreover, storing everything as string is not very efficient both on storage and lookup.

